{"h78bfaafag85a4g49ccga47egf88d91e7e021": ["Wait! I - I yield! I yield!", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "77d33738-95aa-fe5c-2f62-55e643e2b8fb"], "h2fcc7acag9830g4091g8306g6caf1f5adc5e": ["Take his head. He won't be putting it to good use.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "67d24136-55e3-ce23-bf11-977f54cfcd5a"], "h07564d81g9f25g4fb0gb82agfdf4bcf885b8": ["I think my point's been made. Come on, I'll help you up.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "2d56a03e-4096-9813-d997-03c389a64a77"], "h7d0c9545g31e3g4c3cgb7ebg449607f7a419": ["Ya lookin' down on me as well? I can get up by myself.", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "046c8e46-f2ac-0cce-e2c9-9af784be0041"], "h5b16b785ga8cag46d4gbd25g295f493af98b": ["I didn't realise we were here to make friends.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "24342c2f-7333-0ce1-4eab-2bbfeddc3ca1"], "hcb8e84f7g5638g40c3g84c3g4352a269af8a": ["Ignore his spite, friend. Mercy is its own reward.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "70131c6c-c3e9-e3f6-375a-6d7b81ad2ed9"], "h600d73b3g017eg4610ga9deg3453bf641f47": ["Excellent. I would like to knock you down again.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "f25c02c0-efcc-18da-927f-cab57a8827d6"], "h32c7d1e0g7492g4fd3gb0cfg2348012aadf5": ["You could've at least let him grovel a little.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "63a804b8-1dbc-647e-2e43-1718457bfff8"], "h326cec36g1e26g448bga1d9g27dd88df06fb": ["Lucky he didn't take the chance to gut you.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "a9fe2ad6-2e49-0789-cde2-ef42fa6d1efd"], "hdac8ae19g9ac4g4b68ga12bg36caf9417b92": ["All that, and you'd give him a hand? You're a fickle one, chief.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "838d48ba-13cf-5b0f-71f9-0e8b9060ec8e"], "hbba0650cga746g461cg8b42g2021cabbe4ea": ["Courtesy is quite wasted on this fellow, I see.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "37cabbef-09e9-d6b5-04fd-ba1d33d6e9d5"], "h4da8fea6g88ecg4aefg8d0eg6200df662ca5": ["You strike your prey, then offer aid? I will never understand your kind.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "18058462-81bb-6d45-ecbb-b0028e1fd24a"], "h2a46eec0gd72cg498bg8cf1gb724b107aa78": ["You strike your prey, then offer aid? Deplorable.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "18058462-81bb-6d45-ecbb-b0028e1fd24a"], "hc5c64285gad56g4dc8g89b3gbd1f815274f2": ["Now. <i>You </i>should kiss <i>my </i>feet.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "1bca55c6-652e-3c0a-f01b-73ec54bf28c3"], "hc5f02c31g842eg4805g9885g95c84bbf016a": ["Yes... yes!", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "d8dca41c-41db-a8b9-24b5-b884e5dc3362"], "h428f9bc6ge01fg479dg8f51gd89ce2d0d13c": ["There... there, I dun it.", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "57c02198-bc83-ac3a-0110-4949fbfafd1c"], "hd32177b6g160fg4cb6g9c84g8de404f6ddd4": ["<i>Leave him grovelling on the ground.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "16ca29ed-0b40-2aab-a298-4b606cac22f6"], "h82480ff0g10adg473egba71g88c13b078e2e": ["Nicely done. I probably couldn't have resisted kicking him in the teeth.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "2131d33e-93cb-3670-af76-5188a3af4666"], "h00d2e40cgdf1fg485cg8b9fg512060a056f0": ["Gah. Arrogant <i>pig</i>.", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "3c023499-38f4-6656-9a86-0deebe680c33"], "h59682b6eg968cg4122ga6dag71cb1018a924": ["Did that make you feel strong? You're more pathetic than he is.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "73aac4a3-581c-438a-f08d-a33fa57b5517"], "h927c4412g7becg4292g878bg2daebdb27779": ["My friend? Your foe is vanquished - it is impolite to let him live.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "232a8d84-8863-1245-6153-f9ec349bbfbc"], "h2c787ee3g06ebg41b4gbd07g13c07ff62958": ["Ha! My, this place is fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "429bfe39-843a-0ea9-ff4b-f9362a06efeb"], "h2e38cf73g8513g417ag8922g3a787afdc2e0": ["This is grim. Grim, grim, grim.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "1ea8ab17-f964-933d-88bb-4757066ba879"], "h52915bfdgec66g46bfgb007gb88ae87e4377": ["Good show. But maybe wash your foot - you've got a bit of goblin spittle right... right there.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "a64194a9-24f5-89d3-e143-dcdb6e0d9e05"], "h88ec3fb2g5051g4fe0ga608gf4629591375d": ["I hope you learned your lesson, young man!", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "2488fd62-dee5-0553-ec17-9151d2b94876"], "h1a7a820bgaa8ag421ag815dg06e5dd82cf3c": ["A fine show of dominance. Almost sweeter than blood. <i>Almost</i>.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "2a23e49b-50eb-4a1a-30cb-ec0e7a18a891"], "h3995777fg138ag4104ga1b0gff40f36f7af9": ["Learned your lesson?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "7cad6462-73ae-00f3-5a90-d6c48880ca10"], "h774d5934g0240g4ae8gbb9fgf1ae11461959": ["Yes... yes! Mercy!", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "ec0a943e-9bab-7468-08cf-842ffd31ceb1"], "hffc3dbd6g7fa4g42f7ga862gb421336d7f70": ["<i>Leave him grovelling on the ground.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "5a0e9431-bab3-beda-a0ba-5fb35b078108"], "h545f12ccg9f33g4239g8beege5fe6259d24b": ["<i>Laugh at his eagerness and finish him off.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "232bec8e-c31c-6d81-b427-55388688fefb"], "h95202747g6a60g44a7gab9dg17757c9b7ea4": ["<i>Ignore his pleading and prepare for the finishing blow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "309e45ad-bba3-d3ee-55e6-5e16200ad9a7"], "h5146ee05g5afag4f48gbbeega47fed0e9550": ["Good. We've had enough party games now, I think.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "26cceb23-42a1-198f-ffd1-12a84cba64c1"], "h0fdfb74dg136eg4cf1ga1cbg129399977238": ["Help! H - help me!", "0c3404d4-af6f-4c3c-8873-101a79cc4d86", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "6fd66f1c-d72e-5d49-929f-ec893e9c7d26"], "hf788cfcagc7c8g46f9gb8fbg98ed3ac890aa": ["He surrendered - leave him be.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "6581001b-1c05-3cc5-a4f8-8a2dbb865b06"], "he0e574ecgbc95g4847ga99fg5f4f42f78f39": ["Die well, little sticky one.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "fa5d62cd-513a-975e-c9db-7eb1e1e20a73"], "hfc8b3d08gaa5cg426cgb1c0g27fd019dc3f7": ["Thank you. I thought you were never going to shut him up.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "bcd71ab3-7973-81b0-e37b-cae36a3f0ce4"], "h0d07d05bgdf70g4deag8e73g106541120180": ["One more down.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "1cd56032-08a0-caaf-94a8-642ab8950eb0"], "h24ab47c8ga241g42c6ga812gd951122a2b03": ["No better goblin than a dead one, they say. Or they should.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "5b5522ed-6ef1-0e20-8763-d2753452f9b1"], "hc9502542g75bcg4fc5ga424g02fe74ce7f03": ["Mercy is not your strong suit, is it?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "49b480d1-06f7-45f5-b073-8badaa282d9e"], "h2000f280g9f4bg42eega560g377ce5ee0ade": ["A fine show of force. The worms shall feast tonight.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "4bc8b491-eda1-8fbe-2399-dfc8ec683045"], "hc677936bg9925g4d08gaef8g81d5015bc992": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "bd2940a1-06d4-3be4-f768-8ce4a8272df3"], "he5a2131agba0ag4f41g85cdg75777fced715": ["Best not leave any loose ends. This one might reward mercy with backstabbing.", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "7ce5f71f-a2ae-a6df-efe6-68bdc6a89979"], "h02654006g2c67g4f4fgb756ga2d782842399": ["Well done. You humiliated a goblin. Let's go.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "644e0c9f-f89e-2fb9-5943-2400e32edafe"], "h6e2baa9fgea51g41a6ga2cbg0a2e44acb32c": ["Stop squealing. We're trying to give you a warrior's death.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "64815b19-7c88-5abd-4341-b6978ce9e801"], "h92548de2ga141g44d1g9f92g549b68721d95": ["Since when has yielding been an option? Gut the little rodent.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "08169dfe-dced-96f6-67db-2ff452ec7f43"], "h0894663ag6033g4b24g82d5gf7d895064258": ["I've seen enough. End this.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "954216bc-d517-d75d-5515-7ec57e58eacf"], "h7eaad82bg6184g45f7gabffg0bdafedda5ca": ["Go on, finish him off.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "0781cb92-ade4-21bc-e290-649e6c9753d1"], "h11882376g13ebg423cgab75g49a40d7e0152": ["How about you make him kiss your feet next? Pungent poetic justice.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_DrunkGoblin_FistFight.html", "e0802f33-8f8e-9200-8752-ed3be76a7f31"]}